data.description: BACK ON MARKET AT NO FAULT TO SELLER.  SELLER OFFERING $5,000 CONCESSION. PLEASE ASK ABOUT 2024 PROPERTY TAX EXEMPTION   Welcome to your dream home! Nestled in the picturesque Middleborough section of Shadowmoss Plantation Golf Club, this property is a true gem. You will not want to miss out on this amazing home that offers a unique blend of luxury and comfort that is hard to find elsewhere. Step inside, and you'll be captivated by the abundance of natural light that fills every room. The dining room boasts exquisite wainscoting, while the second-floor primary bedroom features a charming trey ceiling. The dining room boasts exquisite wainscoting, while the second-floor primary bedroom features a charming trey ceiling. This home has undergone a stunning transformation, featuring newly refreshed exteriors with sleek black gutters, premium LVP flooring, plush new carpets with memory foam carpet pad, and a stylish subway tile backsplash in the kitchen. The Butler's Pantry is a delightful addition, and new light fixtures in the kitchen and dining room add to the home's contemporary charm. All-new ceiling fans also ensure optimal comfort. The in-ground saltwater pool is equipped with a pool heater and multi-stage pump for your year-round enjoyment. From your outdoor oasis enjoy breathtaking sunsets from the second-floor balcony, or bask in the serenity of your private retreat by the in-ground saltwater pool. Mature landscaping and tranquil greenery surround the property, creating a serene ambiance. A new iron fence encloses the yard, complete with two entry gates, Empire Zoysia Sod, an irrigation system, and landscape lighting. With a generous .365-acre lot, there's plenty of space to play, work, and entertain.   This home is not only beautiful but also boasts being eco-friendly and cost-effective, equipped with 35 solar panels. The lease has been fully paid so you can say goodbye to high electric bills. It is maintenance free to the new owners for 13 years! Additionally, a Choice Home Warranty, valid until Feb 2026, transfers to the new owner for added peace of mind. The property is also equipped with two Daikin HVAC units, installed in June 2021, ensuring your comfort in all seasons.  Shadowmoss is a vibrant community only minutes from historic downtown Charleston, beautiful beaches, and numerous parks. Residents also enjoy convenient access to grocery stores, commercial centers, recreational areas, healthcare facilities, and shopping outlets. Everything you need is within easy reach, making this location the perfect blend of nature and convenience.  Don't let this opportunity slip away - make this extraordinary property your own and experience the lifestyle you've always dreamed of. Schedule a showing today to witness the magic of this Middleborough masterpiece. Your dream home is ready and waiting!
